Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Mamma MRI
When I select the radio button 'Lymphadenopathy, unexplained'
Then 'Max. short axis diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Cervical right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cervical left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Parasternal right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Parasternal left' checkbox is enabled
When I enter '10' in 'Max. short axis diameter' input field
And I check 'Cervical right' checkbox
And I check 'Cervical left' checkbox
And I check 'Parasternal right' checkbox
And I check 'Parasternal left' checkbox
And I click on 'Next page' button
Then I'm redirected to Page 08 of Mamma MRI
